🚨GIVEAWAY CLOSED🚨 

Today is National Walking Day! 🚶‍♀️

We know every day is #nationalwalkingday for nurses. 

It’s no secret nurses walk A LOT. 

Some shifts you might be on your feet for the full 8-12 + hours! 

We’ve seen nurses record THOUSANDS of steps on their Apple watches.
